g_odvw_4::intro_card_0::headline: Waanti baayyee barbaachisaan ati baratte maalidha?
g_odvw_4::title: Waanti baayyee barbaachisaan ati baratte maalidha?
g_odvw_4::text_card_0::text: Tokkoon tokkoon keessan bilbila keessaniin, gaaffiif deebii hiriyaa keessanii wajjin geggeessaa, isa booda gaaffiif deebii innimmoo sii wajjin geggeessa.
g_odvw_4::text_card_2::text: Akka hiriyaakee dhageessutti itti dhiyaachuukee mirkaneeffadhu.
g_odvw_4::text_card_7::text: Hin yaadda'in, muraan hundi kuusaa faayaa keessa taa'a.
g_odvw_4::text_card_1::text: Hiriyaakee gaafadhu, "Waanti baayyee barbaachisaan ati waa'ee qopheessa suur-sagalee baratte maalidha?"
g_odvw_4::text_card_4::text: Gaaffiif deebiikeef bakka mataa sirrii kennuu akka qabdu yaadadhu.
g_odvw_4::text_card_6::text: Yoo muraalee baayyee waraabde, maxxansuu keen dura muraa filatte qofa hambisuudhaan kan hafan haqi.
g_odvw_4::clip_card_0::goals[0]: Gaafadhu: Waanti baayyee barbaachisaan ati waa'ee qopheessa suur-sagalee baratte maalidha?
g_odvw_4::text_card_3::text: Sagaleen dudduubaa jeequ baayyeen yoo jiraate, bakka haaraa barbaadi.
